window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>With Princess Amelia set to join their family, Dom knows trouble is brewing with the snooty Elven nobles—and he's not wrong.</b></p> <p>But that's the least of his worries. When darkness strikes at the heart of the Saldara palace, it's no longer clear who Dom and his family can trust.</p> <p>There are more and more sightings of the forbidden ones, including creatures unlike any seen before on Risona, and Dom's band must journey across the kingdoms in a desperate race against time.</p> <p>In <i>The</i> <i>Traveler 6</i>, war with the dark forces is inevitable. Armed with his powerful inventions and runemaking abilities—along with his loyal band of women and followers—will Dom be able to alter its course?</p> <p><i>Narrated in duet style.</i></p>"; 
